+# Hyper-Granular Query E2E Fixtures
+
+These fixtures are generated by `TestHyperGranularE2E_GoldenFixtures`.
+
+The test runs the real Cobra root command and real LangSmith SDK client against
+a deterministic LangSmith-shaped `httptest` server. This keeps the fixtures
+stable while still exercising the same command, flag parsing, client, query,
+filtering, export, and output paths used by the CLI.
+
+Regenerate after intentional output or request-shape changes:
+
+```bash
+UPDATE_HYPER_GRANULAR_FIXTURES=1 GOCACHE=/tmp/go-build GOMODCACHE=/tmp/go-mod-cache go test -count=1 ./internal/cmd -run TestHyperGranularE2E_GoldenFixtures
+```
